WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Namaste, welcome. Let me gently guide you through Buddhi Align.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Begin on the Home dashboard. Breathe, check your Daily Rings, and choose your next mindful step.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
In Karma Yoga, record one heartfelt action and the impact it creates.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
In Bhakti Journal, write one reflection and one gratitude offering.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:26.000
In Motivation and Analytics, review your streak, total entries, and trend charts with clarity.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:31.000
In Settings, tune your language, music, and export or import your data with ease.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:36.000
In Admin, review incidents, experiments, audit logs, and system errors to keep the app serene and strong.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:41.000
A simple rhythm each day: dashboard, two entries, analytics reflection, and one small improvement.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Thank you for watching this quick tour. May your practice stay steady and joyful.
